#CHIP YM3812
#CLOCK 3579545

; OPL Envelope Generator Test
;
; Tests the OPL2/OPL3 envelope generator with varying parameters:
; - Attack Rate (fast, medium, slow)
; - Decay Rate (immediate, gradual)
; - Sustain Level (high, mid, low)
; - Release Rate (fast, medium, slow)
;
; Each operator's envelope is tested independently for accuracy.

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Fast attack, short decay
c4 .

r4

; Slow attack, long decay
c4 . . .

r4

; Medium attack with sustain
c4 . . .

r4

; Staccato (fast release)
c4 . d4 . e4 .

r4

; Sustained pad
c4 . . . . .

r4

r2

#END
